<chapter id="r64-system-requirements" modified="$Date: 2005/12/29 10:58:20 $">

<p>The minimum hardware needed to be able to successfully run Route 64
should be in the order of a 400 Mhz x86 with around 64 MB of memory.</p>

<p>Route 64 requires an
<a href="http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.4.2/download.html">Java Runtime Environment (JRE) version Java 2 v1.4</a>
or better.  Note that the hardware requirements of the JRE also apply and
override the vales given above.</p>

<p>To use the WebStart automatic updates an installation of 
<a href="http://java.sun.com/products/javawebstart/">Java WebStart</a> is 
needed.</p>

</chapter>
